{"tid":2511969,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"晉環買家搶記者電話","createTime":"2021-05-01T10:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T10:19:55.000Z","uid":239336,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ad050a3876f9cd3ed0279d4887bc5f0d448db4ff","tid":2511969,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:18:13.000Z","msg":"路勁黃竹坑站上蓋晉環開售，吸引大批買家前往認購。記者通常都會現場採訪賣樓情況，並訪問買家覺得所購買的樓盤質素如何，或者相關資金多少，如果買家不想接受訪問，其實亦可以拒絕。不過今次本報記者就遇到一名買家搶去記者電話後，再用記者的電話反拍攝記者。<br />\n<br />\n消息指該名女子是晉環的買家，並與其男伴購買了兩伙單位，記者見到買家後，上前禮貌詢問其男伴：「先生，請問可否講兩句？」，該名女子上前並問：「是否想影相？」記者禮貌回應「沒錯」，但不料該名女子突然搶去記者電話，用記者電話拍攝記者並說：「是否這樣（拍照）？」<br />\n<br />\n隨後記者取回電話，該名女子便一言不發急步離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210501/O63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210501%2FO63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE%2F&d=TdbSzDXFtRyzmt3f81zqRHT1AxqF%2FibzLHEE6598sd0%3D&h=18057907\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210501%2FO63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE%2F&h=ee166bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210501/O63VI7Y4IVGFPLWQ5ZB4ATXAVE/</a>"},{"pid":"9c03df86aced24dc92fd29c8949beb2d7c0ff493","tid":2511969,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:18:52.000Z","msg":"未死咩？ 定比人偷咗acc？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fde8b47fa6a019d8c1f38867e2e2b5a82d7c50","tid":2511969,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c03df86aced24dc92fd29c8949beb2d7c0ff493","tid":2511969,"uid":92299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T10:18:52.000Z","msg":"未死咩？ 定比人偷咗acc？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 